VtuneFit inherits from rstan::stanfit in the rstan package

# S4 method for VtuneFit
rawdata(object)

# S4 method for VtuneFit
standata(object)

# S4 method for VtuneFit
bind_fits(sfitlist)

# S4 method for VtuneFit
loo(x, ..., cores = 1)

Arguments

object

object to grab data from.
sfitlist

list of VtuneFit objects
x

VtuneFit object, containing parameters "mu" and "sigma"
cores

int

Details

checkout rstan::stanfit and maybe Rstudio

Methods (by generic)

  • rawdata: extract data used to construct rawdata()

  • standata: extract data passed to stan. can be reused as input to vtf()

  • bind_fits: Bind list of VtuneFit objects into single fit

  • loo: Leave-one-out cross-validation

Slots

rawdata

tbl_df. see example dataset, sub02

standata

list.
